import React, {useState, useEffect} from "react"
function Meme() {
    
    return(
        <main>
            <form className="meme-form">
                <input 
                type="text"
                id="topText"
                name="topText"
                className="top-text"
                />
                        
                <input 
                type="text"
                id="bottomText"
                name="bottomText"
                className="bottom-text"
                placeholder
                />
                <input 
                type="submit"
                id="bottomText"
                name="bottomText"
                className="btn-btn"
                />
                <label>Get meme image</label>

                      
           </form>
        </main>
        
    )
}
export default Meme
